Counties._queryString: `county xasc select distinct county from ppr where county <> `

Years._queryString: `year xasc select distinct year from ppr where year <> `

Region._queryString:
{[s]
	`geo_county xasc select distinct geo_county from ppr where county = s}

Postal._queryString:
{[s]
	`postal_code xasc select distinct postal_code from ppr where county = s}

Playback._queryString:
t: select sale_date.month from ppr where sale_date >  2012.01.01;
`month xasc select distinct month from t

Year._queryString: select distinct year from ppr where year <> `

rents._queryString: select  rents: ceiling(avg(price)) % 770 , numSold:count(x) by county from ppr where year = `$"2017"
